37:14.800 --> 37:15.740
by the Druids

37:15.740 --> 37:18.080
might be very deep-rooted

37:18.080 --> 37:18.560
in Britain

37:18.560 --> 37:19.760
and might be reflected

37:19.760 --> 37:21.620
in buildings like Stonehenge.

37:21.620 --> 37:23.580
Now, whether they were

37:23.580 --> 37:25.140
calling themselves Druids

37:25.140 --> 37:26.700
at that time,

37:26.900 --> 37:27.720
who knows?

37:28.260 --> 37:29.880
But we've got to look

37:29.880 --> 37:30.460
for the roots

37:30.460 --> 37:31.940
of these belief systems

37:31.940 --> 37:33.300
and the roots go back in time.

37:33.580 --> 37:34.840
Would it be fair to say, then,

37:34.840 --> 37:39.080
