Right.

37:58.340 --> 37:59.760
People like Aubrey,

38:00.280 --> 38:01.740
people like Stukley

38:01.740 --> 38:04.180
came up with the idea

38:04.180 --> 38:05.940
that Stonehenge

38:05.940 --> 38:06.500
and Avebury

38:06.500 --> 38:07.540
were the temples

38:07.540 --> 38:08.280
