38:08.780 --> 38:09.880
And that idea

38:09.880 --> 38:11.320
has pervaded

38:11.320 --> 38:14.020
scholarly and less scholarly

38:14.020 --> 38:15.760
thought since then.

38:16.160 --> 38:17.960
Now, what I'm saying...

38:17.960 --> 38:19.140
Archaeologists have come in

38:19.140 --> 38:19.540
and said,

38:19.760 --> 38:20.440
absolute rubbish,

38:20.620 --> 38:21.200
