38:24.960 --> 38:26.160
What I'm saying

38:26.160 --> 38:26.840
with a number

38:26.840 --> 38:27.580
of other archaeologists

38:27.580 --> 38:28.840
is that the roots

38:28.840 --> 38:29.660
