38:29.660 --> 38:31.980
and it's not impossible

38:31.980 --> 38:33.660
that rituals

38:33.660 --> 38:34.660
similar to those

38:34.660 --> 38:35.920
of the Druidic rituals

38:35.920 --> 38:37.000
