41:23.740 --> 41:25.620
that this was an extreme.

41:26.200 --> 41:27.220
This was what you did

41:27.220 --> 41:28.440
when things were going

41:28.440 --> 41:29.760
really got bad

41:29.760 --> 41:31.300
