41:34.860 --> 41:36.000
when things went bad.

41:36.800 --> 41:37.720
I think one of the

41:37.720 --> 41:38.460
interesting things

41:38.460 --> 41:39.360
is that the 18th

41:39.360 --> 41:40.120
